---------[  powerpc iss library 755 v2 ]----------

To perform the build :
    . you should have a gliss distribution (>= 2.0.0) uncompacted
      at the same directory level than this package
    . In the makefile, you may have to tune the configuration section
    . type make in this directory

According to the configuration, you will find the following result:
    . src/libppc.a -- PPC library containing simulator, disassembler, etc
    . include/ppc -- header file for using the library
    . sim/ppc-sim -- PPC simulator
    . disasm/ppc-disasm -- PPC disassembler


To try the iss library :
    . go in the sim directory (cd sim)
    . type ./ppc-sim ../prog/primes
        or ./ppc-sim ../prog/argv ...

Notes :
    . To clean temporary files : make clean
    . To clean all generated files : make distclean

